_sText:
This is a Very VERY simple map. I wansn't bothered with adding lighting to it yet so don't complain about that.

This map is a simple climb knife fight. Where players must climb around the circular fence and knife each other on it.

Jumping off will just kill you so don't ;p

Well have fun and comment on it.

If this map is sucessful I'll probably make it better. Thanks and enjoy

The detail may seem like nothing, but it's the gameplay that makes it very interesting and feels quite different. ;)
